<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>A few weeks ago the ids of tweets got bigger than 2^32.
The problem is that the since_id parameter (e.g. in statusFriendsTimeline) is converted to int. But there's no support in PHP for integers of that size.
Maybe we should simply use strings and check if the string only contains digits.</p>

